Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located within the bustling Austlink Business Park in Belrose, just off the intersection of Mona Vale Road and Forest Way. This site offers easy access to the Northern Beaches, North Shore, and Greater Sydney. 

Amenity in the Austlink Business Park includes a multitude of cafes and the Belrose "Supa Centa".

Available for lease is Unit 6, comprising 726sqm* of high clearance, clear-span warehouse with 359.8sqm* of premium CBD quality office space. The air-conditioned office boasts excellent natural light and an uninterrupted bushland outlook. 

BENEFITS:

* 40-foot container access
* Oversized roller door
* Undercover all-weather awning  
* Clear span warehouse with clearance of 10m+ 
* Premium office space with excellent natural light
* Exclusive use outdoor balcony and courtyard 
* Air-conditioned office with bushland views
* 3 phase power
* Kitchenette and M/F amenities
* Available for occupation May 2021
